Do you think you can be the Mrs. Fan?

276
00:15:15,340 --> 00:15:16,060
Mr. Cheng.

277
00:15:16,220 --> 00:15:16,740
I…

278
00:15:17,100 --> 00:15:18,060
Enough.

279
00:15:19,180 --> 00:15:20,860
Don’t pretend to be poor.

280
00:15:22,660 --> 00:15:23,940
I’m not Fan Lian.

281
00:15:27,340 --> 00:15:28,780
You are really not a good guy.

282
00:15:37,980 --> 00:15:40,140
You’ve known your pregnancy at the beginning, right?

283
00:15:42,860 --> 00:15:44,220
If you really don’t want the child,

284
00:15:45,020 --> 00:15:46,500
you won’t wait till today.

285
00:15:47,620 --> 00:15:48,900
Child is not something

286
00:15:50,220 --> 00:15:53,060
you can find another buyer.

287
00:15:54,620 --> 00:15:56,020
If it’s known by others,

288
00:15:56,700 --> 00:15:58,620
Fan Lian may be scolded or hit

289
00:15:58,620 --> 00:15:59,260
by the family.

290
00:15:59,780 --> 00:16:02,060
And he is still Mr. Fan.

291
00:16:02,980 --> 00:16:04,620
But what can you get?

292
00:16:17,420 --> 00:16:18,180
Okay.

293
00:16:19,860 --> 00:16:20,860
Buy now price.

294
00:16:24,500 --> 00:16:25,180
One hundred thousand.

295
00:16:28,260 --> 00:16:29,540
No matter it’s a baby girl or boy,

296
00:16:30,420 --> 00:16:31,740
give me money once it comes out.

297
00:16:34,220 --> 00:16:35,060
I won’t raise the child.

298
00:16:37,180 --> 00:16:38,500
One hundred thousand.

299
00:16:40,740 --> 00:16:42,780
You think your child is made of gold?

300
00:16:43,540 --> 00:16:45,140
A penny less,

301
00:16:47,140 --> 00:16:48,420
no deal.

302
00:16:51,380 --> 00:16:51,980
Mr. Cheng.

303
00:16:52,620 --> 00:16:54,500
Mrs. Cheng and Miss Cheng are looking for you.

304
00:16:54,900 --> 00:16:56,100
They want you to go home.

305
00:16:56,780 --> 00:16:57,780
Okay.

306
00:17:04,180 --> 00:17:05,099
I have to go.

307
00:17:08,420 --> 00:17:09,660
Think it carefully.

308
00:17:11,540 --> 00:17:13,020
I will come next time.

309
00:17:19,300 --> 00:17:19,859
Fengtai.

310
00:17:20,260 --> 00:17:21,260
How’s it going?

311
00:17:22,780 --> 00:17:25,060
Your child is kidnapped by Zeng Aiyu.

312
00:17:25,420 --> 00:17:26,980
She wants one hundred thousand.

313
00:17:28,660 --> 00:17:30,020
One hundred thousand?

314
00:17:30,140 --> 00:17:31,140
Why is it so expensive?

315
00:17:31,620 --> 00:17:32,820
I don’t want the child.

316
00:17:33,540 --> 00:17:34,100
Fan Lian.

317
00:17:34,100 --> 00:17:35,780
What are you talking about?

318
00:17:36,460 --> 00:17:37,740
Fengtai.

319
00:17:38,740 --> 00:17:39,100
Fengtai.

320
00:17:39,100 --> 00:17:40,180
Don’t get mad.

321
00:17:40,980 --> 00:17:41,620
But Fengtai,

322
00:17:42,220 --> 00:17:44,300
I… I don’t have money.

323
00:17:44,900 --> 00:17:46,540
I beg you, Fengtai.

324
00:17:46,660 --> 00:17:48,540
You, you have to help me.

325
00:17:48,940 --> 00:17:50,100
Please.

326
00:17:53,820 --> 00:17:54,420
Hey.

327
00:17:57,340 --> 00:17:58,940
Fengtai. Fengtai.

328
00:17:59,180 --> 00:18:00,500
You can’t just leave me alone.

329
00:18:07,140 --> 00:18:08,460
What should I do?

330
00:18:13,300 --> 00:18:15,660
Cao Guixiu has intended to get my stuff for some time.

331
00:18:15,820 --> 00:18:17,060
I didn’t reply.

332
00:18:17,380 --> 00:18:19,020
But now he brought a big trouble.

333
00:18:22,700 --> 00:18:23,820
My goodness.

334
00:18:24,500 --> 00:18:26,060
Cao Guixiu and his dad hate each other.

335
00:18:26,820 --> 00:18:28,460
But they can’t make things difficult for you.

336
00:18:30,020 --> 00:18:31,580
That’s a batch of Western medicine.

337
00:18:31,860 --> 00:18:32,780
It’s very important

338
00:18:32,780 --> 00:18:33,740
and no delay is allowed.

339
00:18:36,860 --> 00:18:38,860
Cao Guixiu truly doesn’t know how to behave properly.

340
00:18:39,780 --> 00:18:42,140
It seems I have to help the dad teach his son a lesson.

341
00:18:42,540 --> 00:18:43,860
Don’t do that.

342
00:18:45,380 --> 00:18:47,580
Cao Guixiu has the same temper with his dad.

343
00:18:47,580 --> 00:18:48,660
If you make him angry,

344
00:18:48,660 --> 00:18:50,940
he may destroy the medicine.

345
00:18:51,620 --> 00:18:53,820
After all, they are family.

346
00:18:53,860 --> 00:18:56,460
But Commander Cao will take you for no good.

347
00:18:58,380 --> 00:18:59,380
Believe me.

348
00:19:00,180 --> 00:19:01,380
I will meet him.

349
00:19:08,980 --> 00:19:09,940
Meixin.

350
00:19:11,580 --> 00:19:13,580
Are you taking it as an excuse

351
00:19:13,940 --> 00:19:15,740
to meet Cao Guixiu?

352
00:19:21,540 --> 00:19:22,500
Come here.

353
00:19:36,100 --> 00:19:37,100
Alright.

354
00:19:37,860 --> 00:19:39,940
I know you don’t want to.

355
00:19:41,220 --> 00:19:42,500
You do it all for me.

356
00:19:43,220 --> 00:19:44,620
Thank you.

357
00:19:45,100 --> 00:19:46,980
It’s all up to you.

358
00:19:47,860 --> 00:19:49,340
That’s right.

359
00:19:49,580 --> 00:19:51,140
I will wait and see

360
00:19:52,340 --> 00:19:54,380
your good news.

361
00:19:56,380 --> 00:19:56,980
(Hongde Hospital)

362
00:19:56,980 --> 00:19:58,300
We’ve talked so much.
(Hongde Hospital)

363
00:19:58,300 --> 00:19:58,620
(Hongde Hospital)

364
00:19:58,620 --> 00:19:59,540
What do you think about?
(Hongde Hospital)

365
00:20:05,860 --> 00:20:06,980
Why are you crying?

366
00:20:08,620 --> 00:20:10,460
I’m consulting with you.

367
00:20:12,460 --> 00:20:13,900
I need money

368
00:20:16,460 --> 00:20:18,740
to save my family.

369
00:20:22,900 --> 00:20:23,620
Mr. Cheng.

370
00:20:25,220 --> 00:20:26,740
My family is in trouble.

371
00:20:27,860 --> 00:20:30,260
I need one hundred thousand to help them.

372
00:20:31,780 --> 00:20:33,540
I’ve been leaving home for two years.

373
00:20:35,460 --> 00:20:36,660
I don’t know

374
00:20:36,660 --> 00:20:38,620
what they are now.

375
00:20:47,140 --> 00:20:47,780
Mr. Cheng

376
00:20:49,460 --> 00:20:50,660
I don’t care the amount.

377
00:20:51,940 --> 00:20:54,220
It’s okay for Fan Lian to give me at any amount.

378
00:20:54,780 --> 00:20:56,020
I have to leave here

379
00:20:56,620 --> 00:20:58,220
and collect money to help my family.

380
00:20:59,580 --> 00:21:01,620
Please help me.

381
00:21:01,940 --> 00:21:04,220
I really need the money.

382
00:21:05,060 --> 00:21:06,140
Please.

383
00:21:07,420 --> 00:21:09,540
I don’t have another way.

384
00:21:09,540 --> 00:21:11,900
Mr. Cheng, please help me.

385
00:21:12,020 --> 00:21:13,580
I know you are a good man.

386
00:21:13,740 --> 00:21:15,820
I will give you that money.

387
00:21:22,540 --> 00:21:23,340
Mr. Cheng.

388
00:21:23,860 --> 00:21:25,260
Take care of yourself.

389
00:21:26,060 --> 00:21:27,540
I will help you till you give birth.

390
00:21:34,260 --> 00:21:36,020
Why do you help me?

391
00:21:39,020 --> 00:21:40,780
Everyone has a family.

392
00:21:50,260 --> 00:21:51,380
Don’t you worry

393
00:21:52,900 --> 00:21:54,260
that I may lie to you?

394
00:21:58,020 --> 00:21:59,420
In that case,

395
00:21:59,860 --> 00:22:00,940
I deserve it.

396
00:22:37,260 --> 00:22:38,860
You detained Cheng Fengtai’s stuff?

397
00:22:40,420 --> 00:22:42,460
You are well informed.

398
00:22:45,860 --> 00:22:47,700
Commander will come back in a few days.

399
00:22:47,980 --> 00:22:48,980
If he knows

400
00:22:48,980 --> 00:22:51,340
you detained the stuff that Cheng Fengtai prepared for him,

401
00:22:51,540 --> 00:22:53,220
he will doubt you want to betray him.

402
00:22:53,580 --> 00:22:55,260
If you want to tell him,

403
00:22:55,260 --> 00:22:56,820
call him.

404
00:22:57,340 --> 00:22:58,860
There is no need to wait.

405
00:23:01,220 --> 00:23:04,860
But you didn’t take any actions.

406
00:23:06,620 --> 00:23:08,220
We are of a family.

407
00:23:08,220 --> 00:23:09,540
You dare not.

408
00:23:11,460 --> 00:23:13,860
You are weighing up

409
00:23:14,140 --> 00:23:16,140
whether it’s beneficial by offending me openly.

410
00:23:18,140 --> 00:23:20,460
When your dad died in that very year,

411
00:23:20,820 --> 00:23:23,700
you weighed the benefits of selling yourself,

412
00:23:23,700 --> 00:23:24,620
your brother,

413
00:23:24,860 --> 00:23:27,060
or your underage sister.

414
00:23:28,660 --> 00:23:30,940
Or the waltz.

415
00:23:32,020 --> 00:23:35,300
Dancing with the powerful Commander Cao

416
00:23:35,900 --> 00:23:38,780
or the nobody Childe Cao.

417
00:23:39,420 --> 00:23:41,020
You are decisive.

418
00:23:41,500 --> 00:23:43,020
You only have patience and gentleness

419
00:23:43,700 --> 00:23:45,420
temporarily during weighing.

420
00:23:50,420 --> 00:23:52,580
You still hate me?

421
00:23:53,220 --> 00:23:54,620
You are too serious.

422
00:23:55,980 --> 00:23:57,500
Thanks to your lesson,

423
00:23:58,100 --> 00:24:00,180
I become today’s Mr. Cao.

424
00:24:02,100 --> 00:24:04,220
What a pity! You don’t have a longer term view.

425
00:24:04,340 --> 00:24:06,860
I’m the only son of my dad.

426
00:24:07,980 --> 00:24:10,460
No matter whether we hate each other or not,

427
00:24:11,260 --> 00:24:14,220
all his belongs

428
00:24:15,540 --> 00:24:16,700
will be given to me.

429
00:24:21,300 --> 00:24:22,340
Childe Cao.

430
00:24:23,260 --> 00:24:25,060
You are wrong.

431
00:24:26,100 --> 00:24:27,140
I’m still young

432
00:24:27,780 --> 00:24:28,700
and Commander is, too.

433
00:24:29,260 --> 00:24:31,420
Whether you are the only son of Cao family or not

434
00:24:32,500 --> 00:24:34,060
is still unsure.

435
00:24:48,260 --> 00:24:49,140
Fengtai,

436
00:24:49,300 --> 00:24:50,140
why are you here?

437
00:24:50,140 --> 00:24:51,500
I’m worrying about you.

438
00:24:52,780 --> 00:24:54,180
I’ve arrived for a while,

439
00:24:54,500 --> 00:24:56,580
but I’m not willing

440
00:24:56,740 --> 00:24:58,180
to disturb your dance.

441
00:25:00,060 --> 00:25:01,020
Childe Cao.

442
00:25:01,180 --> 00:25:02,300
Nice to meet you.

443
00:25:08,540 --> 00:25:10,340
I heard that you won praise from Nanking

444
00:25:10,420 --> 00:25:13,300
for your leadership.

445
00:25:13,300 --> 00:25:14,380
Thank you.

446
00:25:15,020 --> 00:25:17,180
But I’ve made no contribution to the country.

447
00:25:17,660 --> 00:25:20,580
It’s just some small deeds.

448
00:25:20,580 --> 00:25:22,020
You are being too modest.

449
00:25:23,700 --> 00:25:24,420
Excuse me.

450
00:25:24,740 --> 00:25:26,060
Please enjoy your chat.

451
00:25:31,060 --> 00:25:32,860
There are so many beauties today.

452
00:25:33,300 --> 00:25:35,780
Are you here for some?

453
00:25:36,060 --> 00:25:38,300
I’ve been married. How can I do that kind of things?

454
00:25:38,620 --> 00:25:39,540
Today, I’m here

455
00:25:39,540 --> 00:25:41,580
specially to bring you the gift.

456
00:25:42,980 --> 00:25:46,100
Meixin told me you are very fond of arms.

457
00:25:46,460 --> 00:25:47,660
I’m a businessman.

458
00:25:47,900 --> 00:25:48,980
It’s useless for me.

459
00:25:49,060 --> 00:25:51,020
I’d better give it to you.

460
00:25:55,740 --> 00:25:58,260
Browning M1910.

461
00:25:59,100 --> 00:26:01,060
It’s just a common gun.

462
00:26:01,740 --> 00:26:03,220
It’s common.

463
00:26:03,740 --> 00:26:05,180
But its former owner is not.

464
00:26:05,820 --> 00:26:07,540
This is a hereditary treasure.

465
00:26:08,540 --> 00:26:09,580
Who is the owner?

466
00:26:10,420 --> 00:26:11,580
Princip.

467
00:26:13,740 --> 00:26:14,860
He killed millions of people

468
00:26:14,940 --> 00:26:16,340
with only one shot.

469
00:26:17,340 --> 00:26:19,820
Yes, it’s a matchless treasure.

470
00:26:21,300 --> 00:26:24,020
Is it really the gun killed Archduke Ferdinand?

471
00:26:25,180 --> 00:26:26,780
You can take a look at it.

472
00:26:40,020 --> 00:26:40,580
(Note 500,000 Cao Guixiu)

473
00:26:40,580 --> 00:26:42,700
Once you return my stuff,
(Note 500,000 Cao Guixiu)

474
00:26:43,260 --> 00:26:44,820
this is yours.

475
00:26:46,540 --> 00:26:49,500
You are so generous.

476
00:26:51,540 --> 00:26:53,060
What if I don’t?

477
00:27:03,940 --> 00:27:05,620
When I studied abroad

478
00:27:05,620 --> 00:27:06,420
in Frunze Military Academy,

479
00:27:06,900 --> 00:27:08,580
I participated in many dancing parties.

480
00:27:09,060 --> 00:27:10,380
But I never danced.

481
00:27:11,860 --> 00:27:13,300
What excited me the most

482
00:27:13,300 --> 00:27:15,340
was the duel after the ball.

483
00:27:16,860 --> 00:27:19,700
The Russian love to do this after drinking.

484
00:27:21,020 --> 00:27:23,100
The winner could not only take beautiful ladies

485
00:27:23,700 --> 00:27:26,500
but also could claim anything from the loser.

486
00:27:29,340 --> 00:27:33,100
You want to have a competition?

487
00:27:33,100 --> 00:27:33,820
Mr. Cheng.

488
00:27:34,740 --> 00:27:35,500
Dare you?

489
00:27:39,540 --> 00:27:40,380
Okay.

490
00:27:40,860 --> 00:27:43,540
But I will select the target.

491
00:27:45,180 --> 00:27:45,980
Mr. Cheng.

492
00:27:46,780 --> 00:27:48,020
Are you ready?

493
00:27:48,140 --> 00:27:49,180
Yes.

494
00:27:49,940 --> 00:27:50,740
Who’s the first?

495
00:27:51,500 --> 00:27:52,700
Up to you.

496
00:28:12,380 --> 00:28:13,220
Mr. Cheng.

497
00:28:14,180 --> 00:28:14,980
Please.

498
00:28:26,980 --> 00:28:28,300
You have a good taste.

499
00:28:28,700 --> 00:28:31,540
This represents the honor of Frunze.

500
00:28:33,300 --> 00:28:35,140
It’s not about taste.

501
00:28:35,460 --> 00:28:37,980
I just chose the one looks good.

502
00:28:39,260 --> 00:28:42,660
You look good.

503
00:28:43,140 --> 00:28:45,660
You even select a gun based on its appearance.

504
00:28:46,980 --> 00:28:47,900
Beauty

505
00:28:48,020 --> 00:28:49,300
is loved by all.

506
00:28:49,820 --> 00:28:51,380
You come from a military family

507
00:28:51,620 --> 00:28:52,820
and you are familiar with various kinds of arms.

508
00:28:53,700 --> 00:28:57,420
It seems that you are living with beauties,

509
00:28:58,540 --> 00:29:00,100
so you won’t feel rare

510
00:29:00,660 --> 00:29:02,260
when you meet beautiful things.

511
00:29:08,660 --> 00:29:09,580
Awesome.

512
00:29:17,860 --> 00:29:18,420
Sir.

513
00:29:18,420 --> 00:29:19,140
I…

514
00:29:24,100 --> 00:29:26,380
You are very brave.

515
00:29:27,940 --> 00:29:29,700
But everyone in the world

516
00:29:30,180 --> 00:29:32,500
is afraid of “all of a sudden”.

517
00:29:33,020 --> 00:29:34,780
Even tigers doze off.

518
00:29:35,300 --> 00:29:36,460
Moreover,

519
00:29:36,660 --> 00:29:40,820
No one can ensure being infallible.

520
00:29:45,460 --> 00:29:46,420
Childe Cao.

521
00:29:47,500 --> 00:29:48,820
The results are the same.

522
00:29:49,060 --> 00:29:51,140
Who is the winner?

523
00:30:06,540 --> 00:30:09,420
I haven’t carried them away after detaining.

524
00:30:09,900 --> 00:30:12,220
It’s still in Warehouse 4

525
00:30:12,300 --> 00:30:13,900
at the railway station.

526
00:30:15,420 --> 00:30:16,260
Then…

527
00:30:16,860 --> 00:30:17,660
Thank you.

528
00:30:18,700 --> 00:30:20,220
Don’t think too much.

529
00:30:20,300 --> 00:30:21,580
I’m not admitting to be defeated.

530
00:30:22,060 --> 00:30:23,700
I just want you to see my sincerity

531
00:30:23,700 --> 00:30:25,820
through this issue.

532
00:30:26,580 --> 00:30:29,300
I don’t need the stuff

533
00:30:30,100 --> 00:30:32,100
but just want to cooperate with you.

534
00:30:32,100 --> 00:30:35,100
Commander is your father.

535
00:30:35,540 --> 00:30:36,620
You can directly ask him

536
00:30:37,020 --> 00:30:38,660
for anything you want.

537
00:30:39,100 --> 00:30:42,420
It’s not necessary to give me a hard time.

538
00:30:42,620 --> 00:30:43,420
People know

539
00:30:43,420 --> 00:30:45,700
we don’t have a good relationship.

540
00:30:46,940 --> 00:30:49,220
The dad takes his son as a thief.

541
00:30:50,300 --> 00:30:52,740
The son doesn’t listen to his dad.

542
00:30:53,460 --> 00:30:55,140
But nobody’s ever asked

543
00:30:55,420 --> 00:30:58,820
why.

544
00:31:03,380 --> 00:31:04,340
The northeast has been occupied.

545
00:31:05,180 --> 00:31:06,660
The frontieris in an emergency.

546
00:31:07,860 --> 00:31:09,780
Commander Cao has changed the banner.

547
00:31:10,420 --> 00:31:13,420
Is it of China

548
00:31:14,580 --> 00:31:17,260
or of Japan?

549
00:31:17,260 --> 00:31:18,260
Childe Cao,

550
00:31:19,060 --> 00:31:20,180
it’s about national affairs.

551
00:31:21,020 --> 00:31:24,420
Don’t talk nonsense.

552
00:31:28,420 --> 00:31:30,300
He’s my dad.

553
00:31:31,540 --> 00:31:32,060
If I didn’t see him

554
00:31:32,060 --> 00:31:34,820
contact the Japanese,

555
00:31:35,460 --> 00:31:37,740
I won’t talk to you about this.

556
00:31:39,020 --> 00:31:40,300
He lost his senses.

557
00:31:41,300 --> 00:31:42,580
But I will be a good man.

558
00:31:49,180 --> 00:31:53,380
Many weapons and medicine were sent to the Northeast.

559
00:31:54,220 --> 00:31:56,620
Commander said it’s for anti-Japanese war.

560
00:31:57,380 --> 00:32:01,020
Now you tell me not.

561
00:32:01,860 --> 00:32:03,060
